.TH HSH 1 "May 2026"

.SH NAME
hsh - simple Unix shell

.SH SYNOPSIS
hsh [command]

.SH DESCRIPTION
A simple shell that reads and executes commands.
Supports interactive and non-interactive mode.

.SH BUILTINS
exit - exits the shell
env - prints the environment

